text:
Taylor Swift

Here's Swift hiking ...backwards? Yes, backwards. After this photo leaked, one fan on Tumblr wrote, "It's like she's doing that test that police officers do to see if you're drunk or not." According to TODAY, Swift responded by posting a dancing "Bridesmaids" GIF that read, "If I was drunk, would I be able to do this?"

She then explained that the real reason she walked backwards was because of the paparazzi: "I saw the guy with the camera and wasn’t in the mood so I hiked the whole trail backward and my security told me when to make turns.
